title: Guezzam Airport (DATG) is now available for Microsoft Flight Simulator (MSFS).
description:
This video explores the newest addition to MSFS: In Guezzam Airport (DATG). It is the second airport introduced to the MSFS marketplace this week, situated in Algeria. Based on available internet information, the airport is no longer open to the public.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
https://youtu.be/64y8zHVG2uY
